<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-08T23:27:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-12-08T23:27:00-05:00" n="128" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d128">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–851: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the United States Representative at the
                                    United Nations</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Austin</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                    <lb/>
                                    <gloss target="#t_niact1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                                    </gloss>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-12-08T23:27:00-05:00">December 8, 1951—11:27 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <gloss target="#t_Gadel2">Gadel</gloss> 396. Re <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 565,<note n="1" xml:id="d128fn1">Regarding <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 565, see the first footnote 1, <ref target="#pg_200">p. 200</ref>.</note> 571. Authorization
                                requested <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 571 granted. In
                                any exercise para 3 discretion Del will wish consider together with
                                other elements whether reaction to negative vote will endanger 36.90
                                this year or make subsequent reduction to 33⅓ more difficult as well
                                as possible consequences US intransigence this issue for overall
                                political objectives this and following <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>’s.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>